com.cisco.dvbu.ps.deploytool.gui.core.module.resource_cache

Class ResourceCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cisco.dvbu.ps.deploytool.gui.core.module.resource_cache.ResourceCache

  • public class ResourceCache
extends java.lang.Object

    Bean object for resource cache module resource cache records. Intended to be serialized/deserialized by Jackson into/from JSON.

    1.0
    Author:
